title: You belong with me {Sims 2}
description: One of my favorite songs by the lovely, the one and only, Taylor Swift. This is the secret music video!!! 3. I REALLY like how it turned out. I had to re-do the prom scene... freaking sims... So, yeah, in the re-do, a couple disappeared. 4. GUEST STARS IN THIS VIDEO. HAHA. They'll appear in maaany more music videos / stories. 5. I know, the football scene? I don't know what you call that sport. In my country, my football is your soccer, and my rugby is your football xD Confusing, ehh? But yeah, THAT SPORT isn't on Sims 2. I had to change it, and the place. I know you don't play football/soccer inside... but I couldn't make it in the outside cause I'd need more sims to make it more real, and it'd become slooow, and I didn't want that. 6. Ahh. The beginning. The first 10 clips more or less... aren't they juuuusssttt like the original video? Please tell me so. I worked SO hard on them. And on the curtains. GOSH! CURTAINS are haaaard to work with. I'm not telling you how I made them move because I don't even know how to explain that xD and you'd get lost 10 seconds after I started explaining x) 7. I really hope you like it. I worked hard on this. I started working on this video... in the first days of December o.O and I upload it now. Why? I didn't have time, I had to work on My Way, and yeah, I was mad at the freaking sims and their freaking school because it was so slow ¬¬ I trieeed to work on Life and Death today. No success. I could only write an ending for Part Four. Hehe... I already have an idea of how the next parts are gonna be like... MWAHAHAH! I'm gonna finish my sandwich. Yummy.
